main event: A civilian observed a bright round white light in the sky in Laredo, Texas on 25 May 1966.
interesting points: The object was noted at about 14 light degrees elevation in the east,It appeared much larger than a star and varied in brightness,The object remained stationary until after daylight,The observer woke up before daylight and thought it was too bright for a star,There were broken clouds and dark weather conditions at the time of the observation.
witness description: Civilian, unknown age, unknown occupation, concerned about seeing a UFO
